HI'tu' rurta, vIrjInya' 'ev
SuDbogh Su'nIm huDmey, bIQtIq Sen'anDowa'
pa' yIn ngo' law' pa' Sormey ngo' puS
yIn chu' law' huD chu' puS; SuStavIS 'o rur SuS

mu' bomqa'lu'bogh:
hats tawmey, juDaq hIDev
DaqwIj 'obe'mo' naDev
vIrjInya' 'ev, huD'a' SoSoy
juDaq hIDev, hats tawmey

gha lubop hoch wov'onmeywIj
ghlIlwI' be' gha, 'ej not bIQ SuD Sovcho
hurgh 'ej lam, chalDaq mIllogh chenmolu'
wovtabogh maS wejwa', SaQtabogh mInDu'

(mu' bomqa'lu'bogh tIbomqa')

ghoghDaj vIHoy; qaStavIS po murItta
jIvaD juwIj hop qawmota wab hevwI'
tawDaq jISeDtavIS, pay' jItIw
'ej wa'hu ju vIpawnIS 'e' vIhar, 'e' vIhar

(cha'logh mu' bomqa'lu'bogh tIbomqa')

juDaq hIDev, hats taw tIlo'
juDaq hIDev, hats taw tIlo'
